{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    },
    {
      "name": "DS_LOKI",
      "label": "Loki",
      "description": "",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "loki",
      "pluginName": "Loki"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "12.3.2"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "logs",
      "name": "Logs",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "loki",
      "name": "Loki",
      "version": "12.3.2"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "stat",
      "name": "Stat",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "timeseries",
      "name": "Time series",
      "version": ""
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan total throughput aplikasi dalam request per detik dari semua endpoint. Gunakan panel ini untuk melihat beban traffic global. Jika nilainya naik tajam, lanjut cek panel RPS by Endpoint untuk tahu route mana yang paling dominan.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Total RPS",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total RPS",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan latensi p95 global dari semua request API. p95 berarti 95% request selesai di bawah nilai ini, sehingga lebih berguna untuk melihat pengalaman user yang lambat dibanding rata-rata. p50/median sering terlalu optimis, sedangkan p99 lebih cocok untuk investigasi detail karena lebih noisy.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.3
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Global p95 Latency",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan jumlah response 5xx per detik. Ini adalah volume absolut server error, berguna untuk melihat apakah backend sedang benar-benar menghasilkan error. Panel ini dipisah dari ratio karena RPS menjawab 'berapa banyak error', sementara ratio menjawab 'berapa persen traffic yang error'.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"5..\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx RPS",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "5xx Error RPS",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan persentase request yang berakhir sebagai 5xx dibanding total traffic. Panel ini penting karena 1 error per detik bisa sangat serius saat traffic kecil, tetapi bisa kecil dampaknya saat traffic besar. Query memakai clamp_min agar tidak error saat traffic sangat rendah atau nol.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.01
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.05
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"5..\"}[1m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\"}[1m])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx Ratio",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "5xx Error Ratio",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan request per detik untuk setiap kombinasi method dan route. Ini panel utama untuk mencari endpoint paling ramai atau endpoint yang traffic-nya tiba-tiba naik. Route memakai pattern Express, bukan raw URL, supaya label tidak meledak karena ID seperti /contacts/1, /contacts/2, dan seterusnya.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (route, method) (rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{method}} {{route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "RPS by Endpoint",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan latensi p95 per endpoint. Gunakan panel ini setelah Global p95 Latency naik untuk menemukan route yang lambat. p95 dipilih sebagai default karena cukup sensitif terhadap tail latency tanpa terlalu noisy seperti p99. Jika butuh investigasi lebih dalam, p50 dan p99 bisa ditambahkan sebagai target tambahan di panel yang sama.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, route, method) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{method}} {{route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "p95 Latency by Endpoint",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan rata-rata latensi seluruh request dalam milidetik. Berbeda dengan p95 yang fokus ke tail latency, average latency berguna untuk melihat tren performa secara umum. Cocok dipasangkan dengan panel p95 untuk mendapatkan gambaran utuh: apakah kenaikan disebabkan oleh semua request melambat (average naik) atau hanya sebagian kecil (p95 naik, average stabil).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "decimals": 1
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [],
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "hideZeros": false,
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "(sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_sum{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m])) / sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m]))) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "Average Latency",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Average Latency (ms)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan distribusi request per detik berdasarkan HTTP status code. Panel ini berguna untuk melihat komposisi traffic secara cepat, misalnya apakah mayoritas 200, mulai banyak 400, atau muncul 500. Untuk tahu endpoint mana yang bermasalah, lanjut ke panel 4xx/5xx RPS by Endpoint.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (status) (rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"$status\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "HTTP {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "RPS by Status",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan 4xx dan 5xx per endpoint dalam request per detik. 4xx biasanya masalah request/client/validasi/auth, sedangkan 5xx biasanya masalah server/dependency. Panel ini sengaja menggabungkan 4xx dan 5xx untuk drilldown endpoint error, tetapi ratio tetap dipisah karena satuannya berbeda.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 18
      },
      "id": 9,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (route, method, status) (rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"$job\",route=~\"$route\",method=~\"$method\",status=~\"4..|5..\",status!=\"429\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}} {{method}} {{route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "4xx/5xx RPS by Endpoint",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan penggunaan memory RSS proses Node.js. RSS adalah total memory yang dipakai proses di level OS, sehingga berguna untuk mendeteksi memory leak atau kenaikan memory setelah traffic tinggi. Jika terus naik tanpa turun setelah traffic selesai, perlu investigasi heap, cache, atau koneksi yang tidak dilepas.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 26
      },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=~\"$job\"}",
          "legendFormat": "RSS memory",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Node.js Memory",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan delay event loop Node.js dalam detik. Mean menunjukkan kondisi rata-rata, sedangkan p99 membantu melihat spike yang bisa membuat request terasa lambat. Jika p99 event loop lag naik bersamaan dengan latency API, kemungkinan proses Node sedang CPU-bound atau ada operasi synchronous yang berat.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 26
      },
      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_mean_seconds{job=~\"$job\"}",
          "legendFormat": "mean",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_p99_seconds{job=~\"$job\"}",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Node.js Event Loop Lag",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan jumlah request yang diblokir oleh rate limiter per detik (semua tier). Jika nilainya > 0, ada endpoint yang melebihi batas rate limit.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.01
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34
      },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(rate_limit_blocked_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Blocked/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Rate Limit Blocked",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan rate limit blocked requests per tier (global, auth, api). Berguna untuk mengidentifikasi tier rate limiter mana yang paling sering memblokir request.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 34
      },
      "id": 14,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-ds"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (tier) (rate(rate_limit_blocked_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{tier}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Rate Limited by Tier",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki-ds"
      },
      "description": "Menampilkan log real-time dari container rest-api yang di-collect oleh Alloy dan dikirim ke Loki. Filter bisa menggunakan query LogQL untuk mencari pola tertentu. Setiap log entry memiliki request_id yang bisa dicocokkan dengan trace di Tempo.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 42
      },
      "id": 12,
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "exact",
        "enableInfiniteScrolling": false,
        "enableLogDetails": false,
        "fontSize": "small",
        "showControls": false,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "syntaxHighlighting": true,
        "timestampResolution": "ms",
        "wrapLogMessage": false
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki-ds"
          },
          "direction": "backward",
          "editorMode": "builder",
          "expr": "{service=\"typescript-restful-api\"} |= `` | json",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Logs",
      "type": "logs"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "5s",
  "schemaVersion": 42,
  "tags": [
    "typescript",
    "express",
    "prometheus",
    "loki"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "typescript-restful-api",
          "value": "typescript-restful-api"
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus-ds"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(http_requests_total, job)",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "label": "Job",
        "multi": true,
        "name": "job",
        "options": [],
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(http_requests_total, job)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "sort": 1,
        "type": "query"
      },
      {
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus-ds"
        },
